{
  "stem": "5644.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I couldn't walk it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we walked three days to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Warsaw, yes, because we only walked in the nighttime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, tree-- bark of the tree and rotten potatoes or something like that, and flowers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We ate flowers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did have enough water, yes, plenty.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because whatever we passed there was a--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, we avoided them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew about them but--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Caught again.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Germans and the Poles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 142,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They took us to a little camp which was a camp where they coll--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 143,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Collected the Jews in the camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 144,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when they got about 300-400, they sent them, again, to the gas chamber-- to the gas--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 145,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We knew--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Warsaw they hold us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 146,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 147,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, [NON-ENGLISH] three.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 148,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where workrooms, all the workrooms of the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now I want to tell you something about happening, who was caught and how caught.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That wasn't a rule or regulation that I kept caught three, and I wouldn't shoot them on the spot, or take him to shoot, or to take him to prison, or to send him immediately.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It wasn't a rule or regulation.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Whoever wants, did whatever he did want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because why didn't they shoot me on the spot there?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 149,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Or take me to a place like [NON-ENGLISH] 5, where they killed the people on the spot?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they sometimes took out of the bunkers, and they'll shoot people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They found them in the street, they shot them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One, why play around?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No, they decided-- the gendarme, the police, [NON-ENGLISH] decided to take us to this camp [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know [NON-ENGLISH], with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He decided that he will take us to the camp or [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 150,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Order, has to be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Order has to be.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
